 Any time I have shipped Anything up to the land of eternal cold, be it
 via the PO, UPS or whomever, there is a box to fill in on the bill of
 laden of stated value of the contents of the item within.

 Every time I have shipped anything, or sold anything the buyer up there
 has pleaded with me to lower the declared value when the item is
 shipped.



